Planned features (as of 2011-09-01):

Try to get cpan_home from CPAN::MyConfig or CPAN::Config instead of
  hard-coding $pkgdetails.

Add an option to honor %_sourcedir and such.

Handle Devel::CheckLib
	e.g. Math-Prime-Util-GMP uses gmp so Requiesgmp and BuildRequiresgmp-devel.

Some moduels aren't getting their test deps pulled in properly.
 Path::Abstract
  Test::Warn
  Test::Exception
  Test::Differences
  MooseX::Method
   Test::Moose

Add option to use local spec file
  for use when having to add patches or massage spec file

Need to generate a full list for dep build order, including those that can be built at the same time

cs-docker
  * create this command to build/run docker instances
  * Make it use Dockerfiles/$distribution and Dockerfiles/$distribution.repo
  * mkdir -p $HOME/cpanspec/$distribution/$package
  * selinux
  * clean up images?
  * Update README.md with Docker stuff
  * ship in cpanspec-docker sub package
  * catch <CTRL>-C

dist-import
  * include ??
  * make --import take a list of srpms

for pkg in perl-MooseX-Method perl-VCI perl-Crypt-Blowfish perl-Tie-EncryptedHash perl-Bytes-Random-Secure perl-Math-Prime-Util-GMP perl-Math-Prime-Util perl-Convert-ASCII-Armour perl-Class-Loader perl-Crypt-Twofish perl-Crypt-RIPEMD160 perl-Crypt-IDEA perl-Crypt-CAST5_PP perl-Alt-Crypt-RSA-BigInt perl-Crypt-OpenPGP perl-Crypt-SMIME perl-Data-HexDump perl-Authen-Radius perl-Devel-StackTrace perl-Email-Date perl-TheSchwartz ; do
 echo "$pkg";
 cd $pkg;
 rhpkg build;
 brew tag-build eng-rhel-7 `rhpkg verrel`;
 brew wait-repo eng-rhel-7-build --build `rhpkg verrel`;
 cd ..;
done

