WTF :: Bugzilla::5.0.1 is supplied by core perl, moving package content to site paths to avoid conflicts.

$ ./cs-docker --build --docker_dir ~/Source/Dockerfiles/ --image eng-rhel-7
$ ./cs-docker --image eng-rhel-7 --file /home/jfearn/public_html/bugzilla-devel-5.0/Bugzilla-5.0.1-1.tar.gz 


